  "title": "Machinist",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Prepare material and tools as stated in the set-up sheet.</li>\n  <li>Set up and operate the CNC Milling and Turning machine.</li>\n  <li>Checking critical features and dimensions.</li>\n  <li>Report on a blunt or broken tool.</li>\n  <li>Report on material requires for production at a low level.</li>\n  <li>Compliance with ISO 14001 objectives.</li>\n  <li>Perform proper maintenance procedures, keeping the machine/tools and workplace clean.</li>\n  <li>Higher Nitec/Nitec with relevant experience.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of hands-on experience for those without Higher Nitec/Nitec</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of CNC lathe and machining process.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in interpreting drawing.</li>\n  <li>Adhere to Environment Health and Safety requirements at the workplace.</li>\n</ul>",
